CCAPS and AidData built the dashboard to combine trends analysis with the most comprehensive collection of geocoded data on aid projects in Africa. The aid dashboard includes three aid datasets: CCAPS' new climate-coded aid data for Malawi geocoded in partnership with AidData; African Development Bank projects continent-wide geocoded by AidData; and World Bank projects continent-wide geocoded through the World Bank-AidData Mapping for Results initiative.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>WWHGD</dcat:keyword>
